t: "frjeu min \"hmra' alasd\" 'iilaa \"almdyn\" biniemat min allah balthwab aljazil wbfdl minh balmnzlt alealyt, waqad azdaduu 'iymanana wyqynana, wadhlu 'aeda'an allh, wfazu balslamt min alqatl walqtal, watabaeuu ridwan allah btaethm lah wlrswlh. wallah dhu fadl eazim ealayhim waealaa ghyrhm"